# Keep Important Files
# ====================

# Ensure we keep essential Unity files
!.gitignore
!*.cs
!*.asmdef
!*.json
!*.md
!*.dll

# Keep specific directories that should be version controlled
!Documentation~/
!Packages/
!src/

# Keep Unity package structure
!Packages/com.unitprojectarchitect.core/
!Packages/com.unitprojectarchitect.core/**/*.cs
!Packages/com.unitprojectarchitect.core/**/*.asmdef
!Packages/com.unitprojectarchitect.core/**/*.json